text: Zekkeishoku (絶景色; Scenery) is the first full-length album by Alice Nine and was released on April 26, 2006. Its limited version comes with a DVD, that contains an additional music video for the song "Fantasy". == Track listing == # Corona (光環) – 5:11 # Velvet (ヴェルヴェット) – 5:15 # Fantasy – 5:27 # 3.2.1.REAL -SE- – 1:09 # Haru, Sakura no Koro (春、さくらの頃; Spring, the Time of Cherry Blossoms) – 5:01 # Dead School Screaming – 3:49 # Kokkai no Kurage -Instrumental- (黒海の海月; Jelly Fish of the Black Sea) – 1:08 # Jelly Fish – 5:37 # World End Anthology (ワールドエンドアンソロジー) – 3:50 # Q.
